<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transportador Escolar</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .menu-icon {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .menu-icon div {
                width: 32px;
                height: 4px;
                background-color: #333;
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

        /* Hero Section */
        section.hero {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-content {
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 40%;
        }

            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin: 0 0 10px;
            }

            .hero-content p {
                color: #555;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .select-box {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

            .select-box select {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
                font-size: 16px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                border-radius: 8px;
                appearance: none;
                -moz-appearance: none;
                -webkit-appearance: none;
                background: white;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .select-box:after {
                content: '\25BC';
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                right: 15px;
                transform: translateY(-50%);
                pointer-events: none;
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #777;
            }

        .hero-image {
            position: relative;
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .hero-image img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                z-index: 1;
            }

            .hero-image .circle {
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                right: 0;
                width: 600px;
                height: 600px;
                background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 153, 255), rgba(0, 0, 255, 0));
                border-radius: 50%;
                transform: translate(50%, -50%);
                z-index: 0;
                pointer-events: none;
            }

        /* Information Section */
        .info-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #E6F0FB;
        }

            .info-section img {
                width: 45%;
                max-width: 600px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                margin-right: 20px;
            }

        .info-text {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Diretores Section */
        .diretores-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

            .diretores-section h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .diretores {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .diretor {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .diretor img {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background-color: #E6F0FB;
            }

            .diretor p {
                margin-top: 10px;
                font-size: 1em;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

        /* FAQ Section */
        .faq-section {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #E6F0FB;
        }

            .faq-section h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .faq {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background-color: #D1E4FF;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .faq-item:hover {
                background-color: #AFCFFF;
            }

            .faq-item h3 {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
        <div class="menu-icon">
            <div></div>
            <div></div>
            <div></div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Encontre aqui seu transportador</h1>
            <p>Lista com todas escolas disponíveis:</p>
            <div class="select-box">
                <select>
                    <option>Escolas...</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x300" alt="Ônibus escolar">
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Information Section -->
    <section class="info-section">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x300" alt="Crianças embarcando no ônibus">
        <div class="info-text">
            <h2>Deseja contratar transporte escolar para seu filho?</h2>
            <p>Atuamos em todas as regiões de São Vicente, oferecendo nossos serviços com profissionais selecionados.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Diretores Section -->
    <section class="diretores-section">
        <h2>DIRETORES</h2>
        <div class="diretores">
            <div class="diretor">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Diego">
                <p>Diego</p>
            </div>
            <div class="diretor">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Alex">
                <p>Alex</p>
            </div>
            <div class="diretor">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Daniela">
                <p>Daniela</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <h2>Perguntas Frequentes</h2>
        <div class="faq">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>O que é ACESV?</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Como selecionamos nossos profissionais?</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Quais os perigos acerca do transporte clandestino?</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Sou condutor, como posso me juntar à ACESV?</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        © 2024 - ACESV <br>
        RUA XXX, Parque YYY - CEP 00000-002 - São Paulo - Brasil
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
